snippet.title: Social Warfare - Steam NextFest Trailer
snippet.description:
Try the game demo here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3205170/Social_Warfare/

Be a troll-for-hire on social media! You will serve in the Social Warfare battalion and promote loyalty to the Great Kingdom of Eternia, while disrupting society in the enemy nation.
